org.cornutum.tcases

Class TcasesIO

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cornutum.tcases.TcasesIO

  • public class TcasesIO
extends Object
    Generates a set of test cases from XML documents that define the system input model, generators, and base tests for a Tcases project.

    • Method Detail

      • getTests

        public static SystemTestDef getTests(InputStream inputDefStream,
                                     InputStream genDefStream,
                                     InputStream baseDefStream)
        Returns test case definitions for the given system input definition, using the given generator set and base test definitions. If genDefStream is null, the default generator is used. If baseDefStream is null, no base test definitions are used.

        Writes an XML document describing the given generator definitions to the given output stream.

      • getTests

        public static SystemTestDef getTests(Project project)
        Returns test case definitions for the system input model, generator set and base test definitions defined by the given Project. If no generator set is specified, the default generator is used. If no base test definitions are specified, new test cases are generated.
